---
title: Pan-Seared Sea Bass and Warm Tomato Salsa with Rosemary Potatoes and Pesto Pea Shoot Salad
description: This delicious Pan-Seared Sea Bass and Warm Tomato Salsa has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-seared-sea-bass-and-warm-tomato-salsa-f9549930-49104f6c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/pan-seared-sea-bass-and-warm-tomato-salsa-626650ba62d0447b58050a8d-de506436.pdf
